title: Vasalil Oru Vennila
subTitle: Ammu, a little girl, runs away from her bungalow as her stepmother physically tortures her. However, the girl finds love and solace in the arms of Kamala, a milk vendor.

title: Ulle Veliye
subTitle: Gajendran, a corrupt police officer, has only one aim in life, making money, but one day gets caught by the anti-corruption authorities. Things change when a woman loses her reputation and her life in order to save him.

title: University
subTitle: A man and a woman connect with each other through a wrong number. Though they talk over the phone regularly and fall in love, they are unaware of the other's identity.

title: Mudhal Mariyadhai
subTitle: A middle-aged upper-caste man, Malaichami, leads an unhappy married life but seeks comfort in a new friendship with a low-caste woman. However, their friendship leads to many rumours in their village.

title: Udan Pirappu
subTitle: Best friends Sathya and Viji are against selling their colony to a land grabber. Their friendship is put to the test after Viji falls in love with Sumathi and marries her.

title: Kaashmora
subTitle: Kaashmora, a fraudster, gets locked inside a haunted bungalow, along with his clan. Soon, the family faces an army of ghosts who will let them leave only if their wishes are granted.

title: Kuppathu Raja
subTitle: Rocket, a slum dweller, sees his life change when he joins forces with a gang leader MG Rajendran to put a stop to crime in their area.

title: Pattikattu Ponniah
